{"tid":2442522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日資SBI證券突轉軚：無意退出香港業務","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T18:52:53.000Z","uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"69967b2f4234c572949f1b0b80e7e540ce6d7955","tid":2442522,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210311/PQBJYN3GDFHUPLAMK2TPFDB2P4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210311%2FPQBJYN3GDFHUPLAMK2TPFDB2P4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=3afac4a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210311%2FPQBJYN3GDFHUPLAMK2TPFDB2P4%2F&h=181d2e19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210311/PQBJYN3GDFHUPLAMK2TPFDB2P4/</a><br />\n<br />\n前香港上市公司、日本最大線上券商思佰益（SBI Holdings）行政總裁北尾吉孝早前接受《金融時報》訪問時指，計劃將公司業務撤出香港，又指「沒有自由，就沒有金融業務」。不過，事隔三日思佰益突然轉軚，於官網以北尾吉孝名義發公告指，從未就撤出香港有任何正式討論，亦無意退出香港業務。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，公司對於《金融時報》3月8日報道有關SBI計劃退出香港業務，感到驚訝及遺憾，重申從未就撤出香港有任何正式討論，亦沒有任何正式的決定。<br />\n<br />\n公告又指，該次與《金融時報》的訪談，主要是討論有關集團致力於大阪國際金融基地與日本地區銀行合作，並希望成為第四大銀行的商業戰略，但 「<span class=\"red\">很遺憾記者根本沒有在文章中提到這些話題，而只著眼於有關香港和倫敦的一些附帶言論</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然公告一再重申無意退出香港業務，但又指即使萬一有上述決定，亦會確保提前與客戶進行充分溝通。"},{"pid":"d23ec92ab35e2f7e8cb8625b97bfbda4b1a647e9","tid":2442522,"uid":125168,"like":74,"dislike":5,"score":69,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db019ed973f611def42cc7696908cd6faead92","tid":2442522,"uid":106,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ce5f0aa0fc6ac2650377d4defae5cf841f62fa","tid":2442522,"uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"40db019ed973f611def42cc7696908cd6faead92","tid":2442522,